PROBLEM STATEMENT

The "Mindful Work" Project Challenge:
Traditional workplace wellness programs fail because they are time-consuming, public, and generic. Employees experience high levels of burnout and physical stress but feel they cannot escape their desks without disrupting workflow.

How Might We:
How might we design an intuitive mobile system that provides instant, private, and AI-personalized sensory relaxation for employees to reduce stress in under 15 minutes?
